00:01:59.360 --> 00:02:00.350
Two challenges?

00:02:00.350 --> 00:02:02.510
Who can tell me?

00:02:02.510 --> 00:02:03.777
Yeah?

00:02:03.777 --> 00:02:04.860
AUDIENCE: Making hydrogen.

00:02:04.860 --> 00:02:05.270
JEFFREY GROSSMAN: Right.

00:02:05.270 --> 00:02:06.350
AUDIENCE: And then storing it.

00:02:06.350 --> 00:02:08.174
JEFFREY GROSSMAN: Why do
