of the material.

00:18:49.080 --> 00:18:49.970
So that's an axis.

00:18:49.970 --> 00:18:51.890
That's a tunability axis.

00:18:51.890 --> 00:18:55.020
Now, why is this interesting--

00:18:55.020 --> 00:18:55.520
to what?

00:18:55.520 --> 00:18:56.360
To our class.

00:18:56.360 --> 00:18:59.550
Why is this interesting
to quantum mechanics?

00:18:59.550 --> 00:19:02.690
Well, because these
are all quantum

00:19:02.690 --> 00:19:04.230
mechanical calculations.

00:19:04.230 --> 00:19:07.280
And you can see that, even just
the different levels theory,

00:19:07.280 --> 00:19:09.650
oh, you now know what some
of these mean, because these

00:19:09.650 --> 00:19:11.060
