00:22:04.710 --> 00:22:07.110
We talked about this on Tuesday.

00:22:07.110 --> 00:22:11.040
I have my atomic
levels, say, S and P.

00:22:11.040 --> 00:22:16.020
And when I bring them
together to form, say,

00:22:16.020 --> 00:22:18.990
a molecule, a dimer,
like H2, well,

00:22:18.990 --> 00:22:22.290
then they can form
combined-- they

00:22:22.290 --> 00:22:24.750
can form molecular orbitals.

00:22:24.750 --> 00:22:26.940
So that's the molecule there.

00:22:26.940 --> 00:22:29.190
