00:23:16.670 --> 00:23:19.190
And they're very-- these
don't just look like this.

00:23:19.190 --> 00:23:23.390
They actually wiggle, which is
what's really cool about that.

00:23:23.390 --> 00:23:25.160
Oh, there's the wiggle.

00:23:25.160 --> 00:23:29.180
Yeah, they wiggle.

00:23:29.180 --> 00:23:34.400
I mean, that-- I just went
