00:23:34.400 --> 00:23:36.920
drawing this a whole
bunch of times.

00:23:36.920 --> 00:23:40.160
And now, I'm saying
they're wiggling.

00:23:40.160 --> 00:23:41.240
So they look like this.

00:23:44.620 --> 00:23:46.820
How is that possible?

00:23:46.820 --> 00:23:49.240
How can an energy level wiggle?

00:23:49.240 --> 00:23:51.972
What's it wiggling into?

00:23:51.972 --> 00:23:53.180
That's what we're getting to.

00:23:53.180 --> 00:23:56.258
That's called reciprocal
space or k-space.

00:23:56.258 --> 00:23:57.800
So that's what we're
going to get to.

00:24:01.090 --> 00:24:05.390
And I think you all know
this, but, of course,

00:24:05.390 --> 00:24:07.790
when you talk about a
